<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8254592>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Curvularia chiangmaiensis (MFLU22-0252, new record) a. Colony from above (on PDA). b. Colony from below (on PDA). c. Sporulated colony with conidial attachments on the mycelium. d. Immature hyphae e. Mature melanized hyphae. f. Hyaline chlamydospores. g. Melanized chlamydospores h. Macronematous conidiogenesis on the conidiophore. i–m. Conidiogenesis. n–s. Conidia. Scale bars: g = 25 μm, d–f, h–l = 20 μm, m–s= 10 μm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8254592/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

